9. Choose the procedure used when the destination contains files with the same names as the pictures selected for upload.
   - Select **YES** to overwrite the existing files.
   - Select **NO** to rename the uploaded files by adding numbers at the ends of the file names (e.g., “DSCF0001_(0).JPG”).

!Overwrite Same File Name

10. Name the FTP server settings. The chosen name will appear in the FTP server list.

!FTP Server Name
